  "body": "The `Artifacts` interface has a `getBuildInfo` method, but this only accepts FQNs. If you want to get a build info from a contract name, you are on your own. We should either:\r\n\r\n- Expand that function to also accept plain contract names\r\n- Add some way to get an FQN from a contract name (that throws the proper error if there's an ambiguity)\r\n\r\nI prefer the second option.",
